{"title":"诗人的梯子","authors":["瓦斯科·波帕"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":9,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人的梯子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔南斯拉夫〕瓦斯科·波帕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在韦萨特大战的前夕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人迪扬巴拉考夫租了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们隔壁的一个房间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他请求我说服我的父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们的那一边墙上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"架起一把梯子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每夜他都提防"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们会来抓他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进集中营"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为率领一支游击队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他被敌人杀死好久之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梯子依然立在它的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在梯子的木档上蔓延着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根圆叶葡萄藤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裘小龙译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}